modules.description: This module implements Git packfile verification, delta resolution, and index generation for low-level Git object processing. It operates on Git objects, packfiles, and index data structures, using Lwt for asynchronous I/O. Functions support verifying packfile integrity from a stream, resolving deltas with a custom loader, generating packfile indexes, and converting targets to pack data with optional compression.

This module handles low-level Git operations including packfile verification, delta resolution, and index generation, using Lwt for asynchronous processing. It works with Git objects, packfiles, and indexes, offering functions to verify packfile integrity from a stream, resolve deltas with a custom loader, generate indexes, and convert targets to compressed pack data. You can validate a packfile as it streams in, resolve complex delta chains efficiently, or build an index for fast access to objects within a pack.
